gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 114, Nets 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Nets, 114-106. Paolo Banchero led Orlando with 21 points (6-6 FG) along with nine assists and three rebounds as Wendell Carter Jr. added 15 points and eight rebounds. Cam Thomas led the Nets with 21 points, eight rebounds, and four assists while Mikal Bridges added 17 points. The Magic snap a two-game skid to improve to 38-28 as the Nets move to 26-40.
